   "source": [
    "The gap between recognized and unrecognized is sharpest in the **\"Some (5–49)\"** and\n",
    "**\"Strong (≥ 50)\"** bands — these rows have adequate history for DBSCAN but their file\n",
    "prices deviate beyond the 0.30 proximity threshold. This pattern points to price drift,\n",
    "new pack sizes, or supplier unit-vs-case mismatches as the primary culprit for the\n",
    "remaining unrecognized population.\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "*See **Proposed Solutions** for concrete strategies to address each root cause.*"
